---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout>
  <section class="py-12 px-4 md:px-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="font-heading text-green-700 text-4xl font-bold mb-4">
      My Work Method
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg mb-10">
      For each project, I build a clear, human, and effective working framework. Here’s how I proceed — and how this site was designed.
    </p>

    <ol class="relative border-l border-green-700 ml-2">
      <li class="mb-10 ml-6">
        <span
          class="absolute -left-3 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 bg-green-700 rounded-full ring-4 ring-white"
        ></span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
          1. Understand the Needs
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          I analyze the expectations of stakeholders and end users. Goals, constraints, target audience… it all starts with listening.
        </p>
        <p>
          Example deliverables:
          <a
            class="text-green-600 hover:underline hover:text-green-700"
            href="examples/persona">persona</a
          >,
          <a
            class="text-green-600 hover:underline hover:text-green-700"
            href="examples/customer-journey-map"
          >
            customer journey map
          </a>
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="mb-10 ml-6">
        <span
          class="absolute -left-3 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 bg-green-700 rounded-full ring-4 ring-white"
        ></span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
          2. Structure and Plan
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          I build a clear architecture for the project, establish a work plan, and use modern tools like ChatGPT to explore ideas effectively.
        </p>
        <p>
          Example deliverable:
          <a
            class="text-green-600 hover:underline hover:text-green-700"
            href="examples/specification"
          >
            site specification
          </a>
        </p>
      </li>

      <li class="mb-10 ml-6">
        <span
          class="absolute -left-3 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 bg-green-700 rounded-full ring-4 ring-white"
        ></span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
          3. Design with Care
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Code, content, design: I develop rigorously, prioritizing accessibility, performance, and clarity. I use Github, Astro, TailwindCSS, TypeScript…
        </p>
        <p>
          Example deliverable:
          <a
            class="text-green-600 hover:underline hover:text-green-700"
            href="https://github.com/jlguenego/jlg-consulting"
            target="_blank"
          >
            the GitHub project for this site
          </a>
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="mb-10 ml-6">
        <span
          class="absolute -left-3 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 bg-green-700 rounded-full ring-4 ring-white"
        ></span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
          4. Adjust and Improve
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          I test, gather feedback, and iterate. What matters is the real user experience, not just the expected outcome.
        </p>
        <p>
          Let's discuss:
          <a
            href="mailto:jlg@jlg-consulting.com"
            class="text-green-600 hover:underline hover:text-green-700"
          >
            jlg@jlg-consulting.com
          </a>
        </p>
        <li class="ml-6">
          <span
            class="absolute -left-3 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 bg-green-700 rounded-full ring-4 ring-white"
          ></span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
            5. Transmit and Support
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Once the project is delivered, I train, explain, and document. The client's autonomy is a priority.
          </p>
        </li>
      </li>
    </ol>

    <div class="mt-12">
      <a
        href="contact"
        class="inline-block bg-green-700 hover:bg-green-800 text-white font-semibold py-3 px-6 rounded transition"
      >
        Let's discuss your project
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>